* [[藤田哲也_(气象学家)|Fujita, T.T.]] (1985). "The Downburst, microburst and macroburst". SMRP Research Paper 210, 122 pp.
* Wilson, James W. and [[羅傑·脇本|Roger M. Wakimoto]] (2001). "The Discovery of the Downburst - TT Fujita's Contribution". [[美國氣象學會通告|Bulletin of the American Meteorological Society]], 82 (1).

